trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDisplayModeCollection class is designed to contain a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDisplayModeCollection som inneholder en samling med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: It is used primarily by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control to manage collections of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects.
trans-unit.target: Det brukes hovedsakelig av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen til å administrere samlinger av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: A display mode is a special view of a Web page that appears when it is assigned as the current display mode on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: En visningsmodus er en spesiell visning av en nettside som vises når det er tilordnet som gjeldende visningsmodus på den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayMode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Display modes are used in the Web Parts control set to create page views in which users can carry out special tasks, such as editing controls, or rearranging the layout of a page.
trans-unit.target: Visningsmodus brukes i webdeler kontrollen å opprette sidevisninger som brukere kan utføre bestemte oppgaver, for eksempel redigere kontroller eller ordne oppsettet for en side.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control defines several display modes, including <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.BrowseDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DesignDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectDisplayMode>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen definerer flere visningsmodus, inkludert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.BrowseDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DesignDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectDisplayMode>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CatalogDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.EditDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DesignDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.BrowseDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The collection of display modes is referenced by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen av visningsmodus refererer til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisplayModes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: On any particular Web page that uses Web Parts controls, only certain display modes are available.
trans-unit.target: Enkelte visningsmodus er tilgjengelige på en bestemt webside som bruker webdeler kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The default browse mode and the design mode are nearly always available, but the other display modes are available only if their corresponding zone types are present on the page.
trans-unit.target: Standard lesemodus og i utformingsmodus er nesten alltid tilgjengelig, men andre Visningsmodiene er bare tilgjengelig hvis de tilsvarende typene sone finnes på siden.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> class overview.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>klassen oversikt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control keeps track of the available display modes on a page with its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen holder oversikt over tilgjengelige visningsmodus på en side med den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: This property references a WebPartDisplayModeCollection object that contains all the supported display modes.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen refererer til et WebPartDisplayModeCollection-objekt som inneholder alle støttede visningsmodi.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDisplayModeCollection class does not have an exposed constructor, so you cannot create your own new instance of it.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDisplayModeCollection har ikke en eksponerte konstruktøren, slik at du ikke kan opprette en ny forekomst av den.

trans-unit.source: If you create a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> object and want it to be part of the collection of supported display modes in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control, you must inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class, override the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A> method, call the base method to create the collection, and then add any custom display modes to the collection by using its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du oppretter en egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekt og det vil være en del av samlingen av støttes visningsmodus i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontroll, må du arve fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>klasse, overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A>, kalle metoden base for å opprette samlingen, og deretter Legg til en egendefinert visningsmodus i samlingen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDisplayModeCollection class has two public properties.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDisplayModeCollection har to offentlige egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IsReadOnly%2A> property is a read-only property that indicates whether the collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IsReadOnly%2A>egenskapen er en skrivebeskyttet egenskap som angir om samlingen er skrivebeskyttet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IsReadOnly%2A>

trans-unit.source: The overloaded <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Item%2A> property provides access to the members of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den overbelastet <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Item%2A>egenskapen gir tilgang til medlemmer i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDisplayModeCollection class also has several methods.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDisplayModeCollection har også flere metoder.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A> method, already mentioned, enables you to add <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A>metoden, allerede er angitt, kan du legge til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekter i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Contains%2A> method determines whether a particular display mode exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Contains%2A>metoden bestemmer om en bestemt visningsmodus finnes i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Contains%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.CopyTo%2A> method copies the collection to an array of objects.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.CopyTo%2A>metoden kopierer samlingen til en matrise av objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IndexOf%2A> method returns the index of a particular display mode within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IndexOf%2A>metoden returnerer indeksen for en bestemt visningsmodus i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Insert%2A> method enables you to insert a display mode object at a particular index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Til slutt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Insert%2A>gjør det mulig å sette inn et objekt for visning-modus i en bestemt indeks i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection.Insert%2A>

trans-unit.source: Adds a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> objektet i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: You can use the Add method to add new <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects to an existing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke Add-metode til å legge til nye <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekter i en eksisterende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: An example of a scenario in which you would do this is when you create a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> class, and you want to add it to the collection of supported display modes on a page.
trans-unit.target: Det er et eksempel på et scenario der du gjør dette når du oppretter en egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>klassen, og du vil legge til samlingen av støttes visningsmodus på en side.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: To do that, you must inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class and override its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A> method, first calling the base method, and then using the Add method to add the custom display mode to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil gjøre dette, må du arve fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>klasse og overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A>metoden først å kalle metoden basis, og deretter bruke Add-metode til å legge til den egendefinerte visningsmodusen samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateDisplayModes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> å legge til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An integer value that indicates where the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> was inserted into the collection.
trans-unit.target: En heltallsverdi som angir hvor den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> ble satt inn i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> object exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om en bestemt <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> objektet finnes i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Contains method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> object and determine whether it is in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Contains lar deg kontrollere en bestemt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekt og finne ut om den er i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> being checked for its existence in a collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> blir kontrollert at eksisterer i en samling.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether value exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En boolsk verdi som angir om value finnes i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Kopierer samlingen til en matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The CopyTo method is useful when you want to create a custom array to programmatically manipulate a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CopyTo er nyttig når du vil opprette en egendefinert matrise for å endre programmatisk et sett med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> objekter kan inneholde kopierte samlingen.

trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir utgangspunkt i matrisen som skal plasseres samlingen innholdet.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer posisjonen for en bestemt medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The IndexOf method is useful if you have multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode> objects, and you need to know the ordinal position (the index) of one object relative to the others.
trans-unit.target: Metoden IndexOf er nyttig hvis du har flere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>objekter, og du må vite ordenstall posisjonen (index) for objekter i forhold til de andre.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode>

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> som et medlem i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir posisjonen til et bestemt objekt i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Inserts a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"></xref> object into the collection at the specified index position.
trans-unit.target: Setter inn en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> objektet i samlingen ved plasseringen angitt indeks.

trans-unit.source: If `index` equals the number of items in the collection, then `value` is appended to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `index` er lik antallet elementer i samlingen deretter `value` legges til slutten av samlingen.

trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir ordenstall posisjonen i samlingen som en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> skal settes inn.

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayMode"> </xref> å sette inn i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om samlingen er skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: The IsReadOnly property value is changed internally by the Web Parts control set as it changes the contents of the collection at different points.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsverdien IsReadOnly endres internt av webdeler kontrollen som er angitt som endres innholdet i samlingen på ulike tidspunkter.

trans-unit.source: For example, after the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control has added all supported display modes to its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A> collection, it internally sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> object to read-only to prevent it from being changed.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel etter den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen er lagt til alle støttede visningsmodus til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A>samling, internt settes i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection>-objekt til skrivebeskyttet for å hindre at den blir endret.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDisplayModeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SupportedDisplayModes%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > There is no mechanism to change this property value from your code, although you can read its value.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Det er ingen mekanisme for å endre denne egenskapsverdien fra koden, selv om du kan lese verdien.
